00:01:07.380 --> 00:01:08.505 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: How have you been?

00:01:08.505 --> 00:01:10.980 align:middle line:10%
>>HANSON: I have been very
well, and very excited,

00:01:10.980 --> 00:01:12.810 align:middle line:10%
